{
  "texts": [
    "One critical area deserving attention is the enhancement of data accessibility.",
    "Investigating strategies to improve access to accurate consumer data, especially for businesses with limited resources, can prove instrumental in overcoming data-related challenges.",
    "Another promising avenue is the exploration of privacy-preserving AI methodologies.",
    "Future research should delve into methods that ensure transparent and ethical data gathering and usage within AI-driven personalization systems, addressing concerns and fostering consumer trust.",
    "Moreover, researchers are encouraged to focus on developing more efficient algorithms that strike a balance between adaptation frequency and relevancy, reducing the resource burden associated with constant adjustments."
  ]
}